<subSubSection id="C1826517073FFF90F7E5F4BF6DFF4B8F" pageId="19" pageNumber="252" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="8927369C073FFF90F7E5F4BF625C4D8C" blockId="19.[2070,2665,2886,3313]" pageId="19" pageNumber="252">
<emphasis id="BBECEA8E073FFF90F7E5F4BF63BD4D65" bold="true" box="[2070,2226,2886,2919]" pageId="19" pageNumber="252">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F74CF4BF61504D65" authority="Merriam, 1892" authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1892" baseAuthorityName="Merriam" baseAuthorityYear="1892" box="[2239,2655,2886,2919]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Geomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="252" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus" species="fumosus">Geomysfumosus Merriam, 1892</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation id="39F03CC1073FFF90F7E4F48C625C4D8C" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3799834305" box="[2071,2387,2933,2958]" pageId="19" pageNumber="252">“Colima City, Mexico.”</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8927369C073FFF90F7E9F46C6DFF4B8F" blockId="19.[2070,2665,2886,3313]" lastBlockId="19.[1458,2664,3319,3469]" pageId="19" pageNumber="252">
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F7E9F46C63BB4DB4" authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1895" box="[2074,2228,2965,2998]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="252" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cratogeomys</taxonomicName>
was regarded as a subgenus of 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F7E4F43963B34DDF" authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1895" box="[2071,2236,3008,3037]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Pappogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="252" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Pappogeomys</taxonomicName>
by R. J. Russell in 1968 but was returned to generic status by R. L.. Honeycuttand S. L. Willams in 1982. Four species of 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F7B7F3CF63D24A51" authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1895" box="[2116,2269,3126,3155]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="252" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cratogeomys</taxonomicName>
recognized by J. L. Patton in 2005 (C. gymnurus, 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F69FF3A761084A79" baseAuthorityName="Merriam" baseAuthorityYear="1902" box="[2412,2567,3166,3195]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="269" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="neglectus">C. neglectus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F5D2F3A7638E4AA0" baseAuthorityName="Merriam" baseAuthorityYear="1895" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="268" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tylorhinus">C. tylorhinus</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F725F37C62424AA0" baseAuthorityName="Goldman" baseAuthorityYear="1939" box="[2262,2381,3205,3234]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="252" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="zinseri">C. zinseri</taxonomicName>
) were synonymized under 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F78AF35162094ACB" baseAuthorityName="Merriam" baseAuthorityYear="1892" box="[2169,2310,3240,3273]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="268" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fumosus">C. fumosus</taxonomicName>
by M. S. Hafner and colleagues in 2004, who also elevated C. planiceps to species status. Molecular studies show 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F7A6F30E63E94B1A" baseAuthorityName="Merriam" baseAuthorityYear="1892" box="[2133,2278,3319,3352]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="268" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fumosus">C. fumosus</taxonomicName>
to be sister to 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F63FF30E61674B1A" authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1895" box="[2508,2664,3319,3352]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Platygeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="252" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="planiceps">C. planiceps</taxonomicName>
and somewhat more distantly related to members of the 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F71CF2E7629F4B3D" baseAuthorityName="Baird" baseAuthorityYear="1852" box="[2287,2448,3358,3391]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="267" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="castanops">C. castanops</taxonomicName>
species group. Together, 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F9BAF2BC6DD54B64" baseAuthorityName="Merriam" baseAuthorityYear="1892" box="[1609,1754,3397,3430]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="268" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fumosus">C. fumosus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F8DFF2BC6CC74B64" authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1895" box="[1836,1992,3397,3430]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Platygeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="252" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="planiceps">C. planiceps</taxonomicName>
constitute the 
<taxonomicName id="4E984D1F073FFF90F75FF2BC62334B64" baseAuthorityName="Merriam" baseAuthorityYear="1892" box="[2220,2364,3397,3430]" class="Mammalia" family="Geomyidae" genus="Cratogeomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="19" pageNumber="268" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fumosus">C. fumosus</taxonomicName>
species group. Four subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C18265170738FF97FF90FEDC68DD4454" pageId="20" pageNumber="253" type="synonymic_list">
<caption id="DDE766140738FF97FF90FEDC68DD4454" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6603895" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6603895" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6603895/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="253" targetBox="[1456,2047,2894,3308]" targetPageId="19">
